Name: Phu thai
Review Text: You walk in and it smells incredible, like the fresh herbs and good quality vegetables. The wife and I have always loved Thai food, and now we can experiment cooking with seasonal veggies and new ingredients I've never heard of before. You leave with a crate of food for $30. How can you beat that?

Name: Phu thai
Review Text: Very friendly people. If you cannot find something they will take you right to it, and if you aren't sure you have the right thing they will help you with that. Very diverse selection of produce, and reasonably priced. I will definitely be going there again!
